  "1886": {
    "Unknown": "THE 25TH ANNIVERSARY OF MR. SPURGEON\u2019S FIRST SERMON IN THE TABERNACLE! \u201cI have preached righteousness in the great congregation: lo, I have not refrained my lips, O Lord, You know. I have not hid Your righteousness within my heart; I have declared Your faithfulness and Your salvation: I have not concealed Your loving-kindness and Your truth from the great congregation. Withhold not Your tender mercies from me, O Lord: let Your loving-kindness and Your truth continually preserve me.\u201d [v_Psa_40_9] [v_Psa_40_10] [v_Psa_40_11]"
  },
  "2": {
    "Unknown": "The Holy Spirit would set before us, in a most emphatic way, the greatness of our Saviour\u2019s saving power, the majesty of his unconditional grace, and the immutability of his faithfulness."
  },
